article.description: — Ty Gordon had 23 points as Nicholls State defeated UC Davis 101-93 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Gordon scores 23 to carry Nicholls St. over UC Davis 101-93
article.linkText: Gordon scores 23 to carry Nicholls St. over UC Davis 101-93
article.story: SANTA CLARA, Calif. -- — Ty Gordon had 23 points as Nicholls State defeated UC Davis 101-93 on Wednesday night. Isaac Johnson had 18 points for Nicholls State (1-0). Jaylen Fornes added 18 points. Najee Garvin had 18 points and nine rebounds. Ezra Manjon scored a career-high 25 points for the Aggies (0-1). Damion Squire scored a career-high 21 points. Kennedy Koehler had 11 points and five assists. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
